*FvwmButtons(6x1, Swallow "mini-term" "Exec exec xterm +cn -T mini-term -bg Grey80")
*FvwmButtons(6x1, Swallow "xconsole" "Exec exec xconsole -bg Grey80 -geometry +0+0")

